Title: Alpha E-Tec Hybrid Packaged Heat Pump System
Description: A packaged heat pump solution helping owners to make moves towards renewable heating, the Alpha E-Tec Hybrid 4kW air source heat pump improves efficiency while also maintaining the reliability of a traditional gas boiler. Comparing available energy prices and checking temperatures to choose the most efficient combination for home heating, the E-Tec Hybrid reduces waste and costs with no need for hands on programming and selection. When needed, hot water can be provided by the system's gas boiler, ensuring comfort and convenience.
